OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJamaica eyes slavery       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Freparations from Tory MP   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Jamaica is considering whether to seek 
OL,6, compensation from a wealthy            
OL,7, Conservative MP for his family's       
OL,8, historical role in slavery.            
OL,10,FRichard Drax's ancestors were pioneers 
OL,11,Fof the sugar and slave trades in the   
OL,12,FCaribbean about 400 years ago.         
OL,14,FThe MP is facing demands to pay        
OL,15,FBarbados for harm caused by slavery at 
OL,16,Fan estate he inherited in the country. 
OL,18,FNow Jamaica's National Council on      
OL,19,FReparations is also examining the case 
OL,20,Ffor pressing Mr Drax for damages.      
